ğŸ’¡ Learning Outcomes
Gained hands-on experience in Natural Language Processing (NLP)

Learned to implement and evaluate text classification models

Understood the importance of feature extraction methods like TF-IDF

Practiced performance tuning to reduce false positives in spam classification

